Repeat: drop next stitch off needle and unravel 4 rows down, picking up Color A stitch from Row 1 below; insert needle into this stitch and under the 4 loose strands of Color B, and knit, catching the 4 loose strands behind the stitch; k3
drop next stitch, unravel and knit Color A stitch from Row 5 below in the same manner as Row 6 was worked, k3
